	<Price>150 gp</Price>
	<Bulk>L</Bulk>
	<Traits>Evocation, Magical</Traits>
	<Usage>worn on 1 hand</Usage>
	<Description>This sharp-taloned &lt;i&gt;+1 striking spiked gauntlet &lt;/i&gt;appears to have been crafted from dragon scales, with claws built from iron. In addition to the typical weapon traits, a &lt;i&gt;Cinderclaw gauntlet&lt;/i&gt; has the versatile S trait.

 On a critical hit, the &lt;i&gt;Cinderclaw gauntlet&lt;/i&gt; deals an additional 1d6 fire damage.

