Each &lt;i&gt;heartstone&lt;/i&gt; is powered by the spirit of a specific night hag. If it’s separated from her for 24 hours (or she’s been dead for 24 hours), it becomes a nonmagical gemstone. A &lt;i&gt;heartstone&lt;/i&gt; allows the hag to use additional occult innate spells: &lt;i&gt;ethereal jaunt&lt;/i&gt; (9th level) and &lt;i&gt;bind soul&lt;/i&gt; at will, and &lt;i&gt;shadow blast&lt;/i&gt; twice per day.

&lt;b&gt;Activate&lt;/b&gt; [[Single Action]] command; &lt;b&gt;Requirements&lt;/b&gt; You must be touching the &lt;i&gt;heartstone&lt;/i&gt;.; &lt;b&gt;Effect&lt;/b&gt; The &lt;i&gt;heartstone&lt;/i&gt; attempts to counteract one disease affecting you (counteract level 5, counteract modifier +18).

