&lt;b&gt;Activate&lt;/b&gt; [[Two Actions]] envision; &lt;b&gt;Frequency&lt;/b&gt; once per hour; &lt;b&gt;Effect&lt;/b&gt; You cast a 4th-level &lt;i&gt;charm&lt;/i&gt; spell (DC 38).</Description>
</Item>
